    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能像对待物体一样操作空旷的空间吗？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Reverie</strong> 是一款以梦境为主题的故事驱动型解谜游戏。<br>在这个世界中，您可以像对待物体一样抓取并移动空旷的空间。<br>通过解谜，探索并发现这个世界的物理法则吧！<br>每个章节都会引入全新的主题和解谜元素！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332600/extras/85058f0d2afb0121f032a74103317e36.poster.avif?t=1772159592\" width=450 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332600/extras/85058f0d2afb0121f032a74103317e36.webm?t=1772159592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332600/extras/85058f0d2afb0121f032a74103317e36.mp4?t=1772159592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在梦境中，您会遇见各种各样的人物和动物。<br>与他们一起冒险，揭开这个世界的秘密吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332600/extras/a2227bf542c25645187bad7ea552e382.avif?t=1772159592\" width=480 height=341 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >提示系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Reverie</strong> 的谜题配备了多种提示。<br>如果在解谜过程中遇到困难，可以按顺序查看从简单到复杂的提示！</p>",
